        <https://w3id.org/italia/real-estate/controlled-vocabulary/StateProperty/TipoDiAccessoImmobile/EVENTO>,
        <https://w3id.org/italia/real-estate/controlled-vocabulary/StateProperty/TipoDiAccessoImmobile/GUIDATO>,
        <https://w3id.org/italia/real-estate/controlled-vocabulary/StateProperty/TipoDiAccessoImmobile/ORARIO>,
