        <https://w3id.org/italia/real-estate/controlled-vocabulary/StateProperty/TipoDiAccessoImmobile/UNIV> ;
    skos:notation "Controlled Vocabulary for Access Types"@en,
        "Vocabolario Controllato dei Tipi di Accesso"@it ;
